latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Lata Didi is no longer in our world and it’s an empty hole that can’t be filled with anyone ever again. I have unknowingly kept her voice close to my self in the happiest and darkest alike, on long drives, on quiet evenings, in love and parting and so many of life’s other shades. I have already missed her in the last decade and I will miss her ever more as she leaves us. Her stories of Riyaz are inspiring for so many students, as me. Strumming this song knowing full well, that to achieve the melody of her sound on my sitar I have a long way ahead. May her soul rest in peace.
#latamangeshkar #sitar #latam

I really miss my cat and her curiosity 🐱 
#sitar #practice #cats #catlife #throwback

latestIgtvVideos.title: Composting ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Sharing with you my composter and how wet waste can easily be converted into aromatic manure. This process has enriched my life and helps me understand the impact we make on our planet home. Also partaking in the 15 year celebrations of @dailydumpcompost whose motto is to make composting a national habit! Join me? Let’s make wet waste into black gold and grow our healthy salads and chillies 🌱
📷 @aparna.mahajan 
#compost #wetwaste #khamba #lovetheplanet #manure #urbancomposting

Happy birthday to my dear guruji @zunainhalim !
